# RaOS Security Gate - Code Owners
# 
# This file defines code ownership for security-critical components.
# Code owners are automatically requested for review when someone opens 
# a pull request that modifies code that they own.
#
# For Security Gate #235 compliance, these approvals are required before
# changes can be merged to protected branches.

